    <item>
      <title>随着风向的转变，对油砂城的野火威胁有所缓解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/wildfire-threat-to-oil-sands-capital-seen-easing-as-winds-shift</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着气温下降和风向转变，野火对加拿大油砂工业非官方首都的威胁预计会减轻，但降雨完全浇灭大火的可能性仍然很小。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/wildfire-threat-to-oil-sands-capital-seen-easing-as-winds-shift</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 16:13:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Uber 将提供机场班车服务，并与 Costco 合作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/uber-to-launch-shuttle-buses-at-airports-concert-venues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[优步科技公司正在推出往返机场、音乐会场馆和体育场馆的班车服务。该配送公司另外宣布，Costco Wholesale Corp. 将作为杂货合作伙伴加入其配送平台 Uber Eats。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/uber-to-launch-shuttle-buses-at-airports-concert-venues</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
