    <item>
      <title>亚马逊员工称他们难以负担食物和房租</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/amazon-warehouse-workers-say-they-struggle-to-afford-food-rent</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司将工资提高到每小时 15 美元五年后，研究人员调查的一半仓库工人表示，他们很难负担足够的食物或住所。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/amazon-warehouse-workers-say-they-struggle-to-afford-food-rent</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Chime 增加了让工人提前领取工资的服务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/fintech-chime-adds-service-letting-workers-tap-paychecks-early</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Chime Financial Inc. 是一家以免费银行服务而闻名的金融科技公司，目前它为消费者提供在收到工资之前提取高达 500 美元的工资的选择。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/fintech-chime-adds-service-letting-workers-tap-paychecks-early</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
